snippet.title: Cat games for cats - How to Play Kittens in cute kitty & funny kitten video
snippet.description:
Cat games for free to play cute kittens and cute cat !
Play Kittens as the games free with cute cats, funny cat and funny cats !
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=klearwing.play.kitten

Oscar the funny cat seems looking for cute kitten, when she heard meow voices from the cat game, she came and played with them. Happy ending~

At first "Play Kittens" is designed as a cute cats touching idle game for human players only, especially those love cats but cannot own or bring at least one by their side. For those who already have many cute kittens or funny cats at home, why not skip this part XD

Oscar showed us the possibility of cat person cooperation in cat games on phone or tablet (serious?), after human players finished the management regrading power up and waiting for next reward, let a funny cat play whack a kitty on screen in front of you... for several seconds only to laugh at :)

Thanks Gaspar for filming us this interesting video. Hope you all enjoy such cold winter joke, happy to try our game or give us a warm thumbs up, which can give us more energy to survive and continue working (=^･ω･^=)

For more information about us, feel free to visit our official site:
http://www.klearwingkingdom.com

Thank you our cat games fans!
See you on Facebook of Play Kittens :
https://facebook.com/playkittens
